Package io.neba.api.spi Description

All interfaces in this package are part of NEBA's Service Provider Interface. OSGi services implementing these interfaces are automatically picked up by by the NEBA core in order to extend NEBA's capabilities. For instance, custom annotations are supported via AnnotatedFieldMapper services.
